104
00:07:05,819 --> 00:07:06,860
Kenapa?

105
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:09,990
Aku sedang tidak ingin bepergian.

106
00:07:10,389 --> 00:07:12,860
Kita tidak bepergian, tapi menemui Jung Hyo.

107
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,230
Jung Hyo?

108
00:07:14,759 --> 00:07:15,829
Kenapa?

109
00:07:16,230 --> 00:07:17,670
Kalian sama-sama salah paham.

110
